class Limiter(object):
    limit = timedelta(seconds = 1)
    last = datetime.now()
    def wait(self):
        """Blocks until self.limit has passed since last call."""
        now = datetime.now()
        dt = now - self.last
        if dt < self.limit:
            sleep_time = (self.limit - dt).seconds
                + float(0.000001) *(self.limit - dt).microseconds
            sleep(sleep_time)
        self.last = datetime.now()
        return dt
